    <h2>Mission</h2>
    <p>To empower Muslim girls in Kirkland and in other states in the future through mentorship, education, and community, fostering confident identities rooted in leadership, companionship, and Islam.</p>
    <h2>Vision</h2>
    <p>A community every Muslim girl feels safe, inspired and supported.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>A nonprofit led by Muslim women, dedicated to nurturing the next generation of empowered faith-driven girls through mentorship, life skills, and sisterhood.</p>
